text: Me: Uhm... this... there! Up there!
Me: It is like in this old noid movies!
Me: So dark and mysterious, hehe...
Me: It reminds me of birds, high in the sky.
Date: But on the other claw...
Date: I once fell off my tree and it was really horrible.
Date: I think I lost my ability to see the color orange that day...
Me: Oh no... That sound awful!
Me: But... How do you see orange things then?
Date: What, in the name of the great chameleon are you doing?
Date: I see them in yellow and red.
